author: wonpoint4
body:
Add new MuonHLT Seed Classifier model files.
These 4 models used  the Patatrack seeds.
Used the Summer21 DY,  Jpsi dataset  for  the training.

The  relevant slides during the Trigger Review  ( https://indico.cern.ch/event/1099590/contributions/4626714/attachments/2357624/4023680/20211202_Run3Review_MUO.pdf )
More recent slides shown in TSG meeting on 12th Jan ( https://indico.cern.ch/event/1111794/contributions/4675065/subcontributions/361352/attachments/2371770/4050772/20220112_LowPtMuonUpdate_JSchulte.pdf )

And this is link of related JIRA ticket.
https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2220
title: Add new MuonHLT Seed Classifier model files
